{"tid":507222,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得兩登已經唔再識合我地呢啲孤獨嘅人圍爐取暖喇？","createTime":"2017-12-23T04:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T05:43:31.000Z","uid":60015,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5916901b181359a01d88a09378ca17dffb0272","tid":507222,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"以前每逢佳節上高登<br />\n我由08年上高登到舊年轉會連登，<br />\n已經喺度經歷過數唔到咁多次節日。<br />\n有時我會覺得自己係上太多高登先搞到自己咁毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實邊關事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係每年聖誕即使我冇人約成日上足高登都唔會覺得頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我覺得高登真係有班同我差唔多咁孤獨同我差唔多咁撚樣衰咁撚矮咁撚窮<br />\n一樣係冇人約，碌電話想揾一個人出嚟食餐飯都揾唔到嘅毒撚可以喺高登度開po吹水圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老實講真係有種高登有愛嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家講真嗰句兩登仲邊有孤獨嘅人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMk仔小學雞入侵連登<br />\n而家連我隔離屋嗰個小學生都上緊連登<br />\n仲成日話所有女人都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想圍爐取暖都取唔到啦<br />\n最後送俾大家<br />\n小肥-高登歌<br />\n懷緬下以前高登毒撚圍爐圍佳節嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KfBDwZZUF34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKfBDwZZUF34&d=YMjKz3cQ%2Fky9YqE0tBko1ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d4e430ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KfBDwZZUF34</a>"},{"pid":"c2a7149ed2384b65a2a98c46f3df41a7f35383e6","tid":507222,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12545745011283038b25bbf226b68c7468329a0","tid":507222,"uid":23170,"like":8,"dislike":20,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，女人唔係雞係乜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},